 Hopefully this does not break latex2html.

 Patches for gcc 4.0 compatibility thanks to Matt Sachs.

 Security patches thanks to Tomoaki Okayama:
  CVE-2005-2471: netpbm-10.25-CAN-2005-2471.patch             (from RedHat)
